---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">About PocketBurrito</h1>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          PocketBurrito is a curated tech deals site. We sift through thousands of products on Amazon so you don't have to — and we only recommend the stuff that's actually worth your money.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">How We Pick Products</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🔍</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Research</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">We compare specs, read reviews, and test where possible.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">⭐</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Rating Check</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Only products with 4+ stars and solid review counts make the cut.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">💰</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Value First</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">We prioritize price-to-performance — not just the most expensive option.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">✅</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Honest Picks</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">We earn a small commission through Amazon, but our recommendations are genuine.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">Other Projects</h2>
        <p>
          Check out <a href="https://howmuchwaterdidIwaste.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 underline transition">howmuchwaterdidIwaste.com</a> — a fun tool that calculates how much water you wasted today. It's a quick eye-opener on water consumption habits.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">Follow Us</h2>
        <p>
          We post daily tech picks and deals on Twitter. Follow
          <a href="https://x.com/TechinSeconds" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 underline transition">@TechinSeconds</a>
          to stay in the loop.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-orange-500/20 rounded-xl p-5 mt-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
            <strong class="text-gray-300">Affiliate Disclosure:</strong> PocketBurrito is a participant in the Amazon Associates Program. When you buy through our links, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the site running and continue finding great deals.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
